On Wed, May 30 2001, Steve Whitehouse wrote:
> +	if (PageHighMem(page))
> +		offset = (int)bh->b_data;
> +	else
> +		offset = (int)bh->b_data - (int)page_address(page);
Side note:
	offset = bh_offset(bh);
will handle this nicely for you. No need for (nasty) casting and
checking for highmem pages.
